---
title: Plant-Based Crumbed Chicken & Korean Sauce with Sesame Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: Plant-based crumbed chicken is so eye catching that we can’t refuse, especially if you’re serving with a moreish garlic rice
and a sauce that’s the talk of the town. There’s no way anyone could miss this dinner!
